INSTALLATION:

    $ perl Makefile.PL
    $ make
    $ make test
    $ sudo make install

RUN:

    $ plackup bin/app.psgi

EXAMPLE:

    a) Dancer2 Cookbook showing the power of Dancer2.
       https://github.com/manwar/dancer2-cookbook

    b) Fully functional website using Dancer2, Template toolkit.
       https://github.com/manwar/www.manwar.org
